#. Tag: title
#: fundamentals.docbook:8
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Fundamentals"
msgstr "Osnove"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:10
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have ever used a text editor, you will have no problem using &kate;. "
"In the next two sections, <link linkend=\"starting-kate\">Starting &kate; </"
"link> and in <link linkend=\"working-with-kate\">Working with &kate;</link>, "
"we will show you everything you need to get up and running quickly."
msgstr ""
"Če ste kdaj uporabljali urejevalnik besedil, ne boste imeli težav pri "
"uporabi &kate;. V naslednjih dveh razdelkih <link linkend=\"starting-kate"
"\">Zagon &kate; </link> in v <link linkend=\"working-with-kate\">Delo z "
"&kate;</link> vam bomo pokazali vse, kar potrebujete, da hitro začnete "
"delovati."

#. Tag: title
#: fundamentals.docbook:19
#, no-c-format
msgid "Starting &kate;"
msgstr "Zagon &kate;"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:21
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can start &kate; from the application launcher or from the command line."
msgstr "Lahko zaženete &kate; iz zaganjalnika aplikacij ali iz ukazne vrstice."

#. Tag: title
#: fundamentals.docbook:27
#, no-c-format
msgid "From the Menu"
msgstr "Iz menuja"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:28
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Open the &kde; program menu by clicking on the application launcher icon on "
"the toolbar at the bottom left of your screen. This will raise a menu. Move "
"your cursor up the menu to the <menuchoice><guimenu>Applications</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Utilities</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Advanced Text Editor "
"&kate;</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Odprite &kde; programski meni tako, da kliknete ikono zaganjalnika aplikacij "
"v orodni vrstici v spodnjem levem kotu zaslona. To bo dvignilo meni. "
"Premaknite kazalec navzgor po meniju do menijske postavke "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Aplikacije</guimenu><guisubmenu>Pripomočki</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Napredni urejevalnik besedil &kate;</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: fundamentals.docbook:39
#, no-c-format
msgid "From the Command Line"
msgstr "Iz ukazne vrstice"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can start &kate; by typing its name on the command line. If you give it "
"a file name, as in the example below, it will open or create that file."
msgstr ""
"&kate; lahko poženete tako, da vtipkate ime programa v ukazno vrstico. Če "
"podate še ime datoteke, kot v spodnjem primeru, bo ta datoteka odprta ali pa "
"ustvarjena."

#. Tag: screen
#: fundamentals.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<prompt>%</prompt><userinput><command>kate</command> "
"<option><replaceable>myfile.txt</replaceable></option></userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<prompt>%</prompt><userinput><command>kate</command> "
"<option><replaceable>myfile.txt</replaceable></option></userinput>"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have an active connection, and permission, you can take advantage of "
"&kde;'s network transparency to open files on the internet."
msgstr ""
"Če imate aktivno povezavo in dovoljenja, lahko izkoristite omrežno "
"preglednost &kde; in odprete datoteke v internetu."

#. Tag: screen
#: fundamentals.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<prompt>%</prompt><userinput><command>kate</command> "
"<option><replaceable>&kde-ftp;README</replaceable></option></userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<prompt>%</prompt><userinput><command>kate</command> "
"<option><replaceable>&kde-ftp;PREBERI ME</replaceable></option></userinput>"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To change the directory for temporary files, which defaults to <filename "
"class=\"directory\">/tmp</filename> set the <envar>TMPDIR</envar> "
"environment variable before starting &kate;, &eg;"
msgstr ""
"Če želite spremeniti imenik za začasne datoteke, ki je privzeto <filename "
"class=\"directory\">/tmp</filename>, nastavite spremenljivko okolja "
"<envar>TMPDIR</envar>, preden zaženete &kate;, &eg;"

#. Tag: screen
#: fundamentals.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<prompt>%</prompt><userinput><command>mkdir</command> /tmp/kate -p &amp;"
"&amp; export TMPDIR=/tmp/kate &amp;&amp; kate</userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<prompt>%</prompt><userinput><command>mkdir</command> /tmp/kate -p &amp;"
"&amp; izvoz TMPDIR=/tmp/kate &amp;&amp; kate</userinput>"

#. Tag: title
#: fundamentals.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid "Command Line Options"
msgstr "Možnosti ukazne vrstice"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kate; accepts following command line options:"
msgstr "&kate; sprejme naslednje možnosti ukazne vrstice:"

#. Tag: userinput
#: fundamentals.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>kate</command> <option>--help</option>"
msgstr "<command>kate</command> <option>--help</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid "This lists the options available at the command line."
msgstr "To navaja možnosti, ki so na voljo v ukazni vrstici."

#. Tag: userinput
#: fundamentals.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>kate</command> <option>-s</option> <option>--start</option> "
"<parameter>name</parameter>"
msgstr ""
"<command>kate</command> <option>-s</option> <option>--začetek</option> "
"<parameter>ime</parameter>"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Starts &kate; with the session <parameter>name</parameter>. The session is "
"created if it does not exist already. If a &kate; instance running the "
"specified session exists, the specified files are loaded in that instance."
msgstr ""
"Zažene &kate; z <parameter>ime</parameter> seje. Seja je ustvarjena, če še "
"ne obstaja. Če &kate; primerek, ki izvaja določeno sejo, obstaja, so "
"navedene datoteke naložene v tem primeru."

#. Tag: userinput
#: fundamentals.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>kate</command> <option>-p</option> <option>--pid</option> "
"<parameter>PID</parameter>"
msgstr ""
"<command>kate</command> <option>-p</option> <option>--pid</option> "
"<parameter>PID</parameter>"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid "Only reuses an instance with the specified PID (Process ID)."
msgstr "Ponovno uporabi samo primerek z navedenim PID (ID procesa)."

#. Tag: userinput
#: fundamentals.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>kate</command> <option>-e</option> <option>--encoding</option> "
"<parameter>encoding</parameter> <parameter>URL</parameter>"
msgstr ""
"<command>kate</command> <option>-e</option> <option>--kodiranje</option> "
"<parameter>kodiranje</parameter> <parameter>URL</parameter>"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid "Uses the specified encoding for the document."
msgstr "Uporablja navedeno kodiranje za dokument."

#. Tag: userinput
#: fundamentals.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>kate</command> <option>-l</option> <option>--line</option> "
"<parameter>line</parameter> <parameter>URL</parameter>"
msgstr ""
"<command>kate</command> <option>-l</option> <option>--vrstica</option> "
"<parameter>vrstica</parameter> <parameter>URL</parameter>"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid "Navigates to the specified line after opening the document."
msgstr "Po odprtju dokumenta se pomakne do določene vrstice."

#. Tag: userinput
#: fundamentals.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>kate</command> <option>-c</option> <option>--column</option> "
"<parameter>column</parameter> <parameter>URL</parameter>"
msgstr ""
"<command>kate</command> <option>-c</option> <option>--stolpec</option> "
"<parameter>stolpec</parameter> <parameter>URL</parameter>"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid "Navigates to the specified column after opening the document."
msgstr "Po odprtju dokumenta se pomakne do določenega stolpca."

#. Tag: userinput
#: fundamentals.docbook:128
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>kate</command> <option>-i</option> <option>--stdin</option>"
msgstr "<command>kate</command> <option>-i</option> <option>--stdin</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Reads the document content from STDIN. This is similar to the common option "
"<option>-</option> used in many command line programs, and allows you to "
"pipe command output into &kate;."
msgstr ""
"Prebere vsebino dokumenta iz STDIN. To je podobno običajni možnosti <option>-"
"</option>, ki se uporablja v številnih programih z ukazno vrstico, in vam "
"omogoča, da izhod ukaza prenesete v &kate;."

#. Tag: userinput
#: fundamentals.docbook:136
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>kate</command> <option>--startanon</option>"
msgstr "<command>kate</command> <option>--startanon</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:138
#, no-c-format
msgid "Start &kate; with a new anonymous session, implies <option>-n</option>."
msgstr "Zaženi &kate; z novo anonimno sejo pomeni <option>-n</option>."

#. Tag: userinput
#: fundamentals.docbook:143
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>kate</command> <option>-n</option> <option>--new</option>"
msgstr "<command>kate</command> <option>-n</option> <option>--novo</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:145
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Force start of a new &kate; instance (is ignored if <option>start</option> "
"is used and another &kate; instance already has the given session opened), "
"forced if no parameters and no URLs are given at all."
msgstr ""
"Vsili zagon novega &kate; primerek (je prezrt, če je uporabljen "
"<option>start</option> in je drug primerek &kate; že odprl dano sejo), "
"vsiljen, če niso podani nobeni parametri ali URL-ji."

#. Tag: userinput
#: fundamentals.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>kate</command> <option>-b</option> <option>--block</option>"
msgstr ""
"<command>kate</command> <option>-b</option> <option>--blokiraj</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If using an already running &kate; instance, block until it exits, if URLs "
"given to open."
msgstr ""
"Če uporabljate že delujoč &kate; primer, blokira, dokler ne zapre, če so URL-"
"ji dani za odpiranje."

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:155
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can use &kate; with this option as editor for typing in commit messages "
"for version control systems like &git; or <application>Subversion</"
"application>. These systems expect to block the editor till you have entered "
"your message, because they then open the temporary file, which would be "
"empty if &kate; immediately returned to the caller."
msgstr ""
"Lahko uporabite &kate; s to možnostjo kot urejevalnik za vnašanje sporočil o "
"objavi za sisteme za nadzor različic, kot je &git; ali "
"<application>Subversion</application>. Ti sistemi pričakujejo, da bodo "
"blokirali urejevalnik, dokler ne vnesete svojega sporočila, ker nato odprejo "
"začasno datoteko, ki bi bila prazna, če &kate; takoj vrnil klicatelju."

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option is also needed with KIO (&kde; Input/Output), if you open a "
"remote file (which has been downloaded to a temporary) and should be "
"reuploaded, after you saved it."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost je potrebna tudi pri KIO (&kde; Vhod/Izhod), če odprete oddaljeno "
"datoteko (ki je bila prenesena v začasno) in bi jo morali znova naložiti, "
"potem ko ste jo shranili."

#. Tag: userinput
#: fundamentals.docbook:168
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>kate</command> <option>--tempfile</option>"
msgstr "<command>kate</command> <option>--tempfile</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:170
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When used, the specified files are treated as temporary files and deleted "
"(if they are local files and you have sufficient permissions) when closed, "
"unless they were modified since they were opened."
msgstr ""
"Ko se uporabljajo, se navedene datoteke obravnavajo kot začasne datoteke in "
"se ob zaprtju izbrišejo (če so lokalne datoteke in imate zadostna "
"dovoljenja), razen če so bile spremenjene, odkar so bile odprte."

#. Tag: userinput
#: fundamentals.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>kate</command> <option>--desktopfile</option> <parameter>filename</"
"parameter>"
msgstr ""
"<command>kate</command> <option>--namizna datoteka</option> <parameter>ime "
"datoteke</parameter>"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:178
#, no-c-format
msgid "The base file name of the desktop entry for this application."
msgstr "Osnovno ime datoteke vnosa namizja za to aplikacijo."

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:179
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is in particular useful for wrapper applications and applications "
"having in general multiple desktop files. Thus each desktop file can have "
"its own command line for the <option>Exec</option> entry."
msgstr ""
"To je še posebej uporabno za aplikacije ovojnice in aplikacije, ki imajo na "
"splošno več namiznih datotek. Tako ima lahko vsaka namizna datoteka svojo "
"ukazno vrstico za vnos <option>Exec</option>."

#. Tag: userinput
#: fundamentals.docbook:186
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>kate</command> <option>--author</option>"
msgstr "<command>kate</command> <option>--avtor</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:189
#, no-c-format
msgid "Lists &kate;'s authors in the terminal window."
msgstr "Našteje avtorje &kate; v terminalskem oknu."

#. Tag: userinput
#: fundamentals.docbook:196
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>kate</command> <option>-v</option> <option>--version</option>"
msgstr "<command>kate</command> <option>-v</option> <option>--verzija</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:199
#, no-c-format
msgid "Lists version information for &kate;."
msgstr "Navaja informacije o različici &kate;."

#. Tag: userinput
#: fundamentals.docbook:206
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>kate</command> <option>--license</option>"
msgstr "<command>kate</command> <option>--licenca</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:209
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shows license information."
msgstr "Prikaže informacije o licenci."

#. Tag: title
#: fundamentals.docbook:220
#, no-c-format
msgid "Drag and Drop"
msgstr "Povleci in spusti"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:221
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kate; uses the &kde; Drag and Drop protocol. Files may be dragged and "
"dropped onto &kate; from the Desktop, the filemanager &dolphin; or some "
"remote &FTP; site opened in one of &dolphin;'s windows."
msgstr ""
"&kate; uporablja &kde; Protokol povleci in spusti. Datoteke lahko povlečete "
"in spustite na &kate; z namizja, upravitelj datotek &dolphin; ali kakšen "
"oddaljeni &FTP; spletno mesto, odprto v enem od oken &dolphin;."

#. Tag: title
#: fundamentals.docbook:230
#, no-c-format
msgid "Working with &kate;"
msgstr "Delo s &kate;"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:231
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"quick-start\">Quick Start</link> will show you how to toggle "
"four simple options that will let you configure some of &kate;'s more "
"powerful features right away. <link linkend=\"keystroke-commands\"> "
"Shortcuts</link> lays out some of the default keystroke shortcuts for those "
"who can't or don't want to use a mouse."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"quick-start\">Hitri začetek</link> vam bo pokazal, kako "
"preklapljate med štirimi preprostimi možnostmi, ki vam bodo omogočile, da "
"takoj konfigurirate nekatere zmogljivejše funkcije &kate;. <link linkend="
"\"keystroke-commands\"> Bližnjice</link> prikazuje nekaj privzetih bližnjic "
"za tipke za tiste, ki ne morejo ali nočejo uporabljati miške."

#. Tag: title
#: fundamentals.docbook:240
#, no-c-format
msgid "Quick Start"
msgstr "Hiter start"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:242
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This section will describe some of the items on the <guimenu>View</guimenu> "
"menu so that you can quickly configure &kate; to work the way you want it."
msgstr ""
"V tem razdelku so opisani nekateri elementi v meniju <guimenu>Pogled</"
"guimenu>, tako da lahko hitro konfigurirate &kate; delati tako, kot želite."

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:248
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you start &kate; for the first time you will see two windows with white "
"backgrounds. Above the two windows is a toolbar with the usual labeled "
"icons. And above that, a menubar."
msgstr ""
"Ko zaženete &kate; prvič boste videli dve okni z belim ozadjem. Nad oknoma "
"je orodna vrstica z običajnimi označenimi ikonami. In nad tem menijska "
"vrstica."

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:253
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The left-hand window is a side bar. It combines the <guilabel>Documents</"
"guilabel> and <guilabel>Filesystem Browser</guilabel> windows. Switch "
"between the two by clicking on the tabs to the left of the window."
msgstr ""
"Levo okno je stranska vrstica. Združuje okni <guilabel>Dokumenti</guilabel> "
"in <guilabel>Brskalnik datotečnega sistema</guilabel>. Med obema "
"preklapljajte s klikom na zavihke na levi strani okna."

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:258
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you've started &kate; with a file, the right-hand window will show the "
"file you are editing and the <guilabel>Documents</guilabel> on the side bar "
"will show the name of the file. Use the <guilabel>Filesystem Browser</"
"guilabel> window to open files."
msgstr ""
"Če ste zagnali &kate; z datoteko bo v desnem oknu prikazana datoteka, ki jo "
"urejate, <guilabel>Dokumenti</guilabel> v stranski vrstici pa bo prikazano "
"ime datoteke. Za odpiranje datotek uporabite okno <guilabel>Brskalnik "
"datotečnega sistema</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:264
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can toggle all sidebar windows on and off in <menuchoice><guimenu>View</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Tool Views</guisubmenu></menuchoice> menu or use "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;&Shift;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo>. "
"This menu offers you your first glimpse into &kate;'s power and flexibility."
msgstr ""
"Vsa okna stranske vrstice lahko vklopite in izklopite v meniju "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guisubmenu>Pogledi orodij</"
"guisubmenu></menuchoice> ali uporabite <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;"
"&Shift;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo>. Ta meni vam ponuja prvi vpogled v moč "
"in prilagodljivost &kate;."

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:272
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In <guisubmenu>Tool Views</guisubmenu> you have a list of all enabled "
"plugins. Click the checkbox in front of each item or click with the &LMB; on "
"the tool buttons in the sidebar to toggle this tool view on and off."
msgstr ""
"V <guisubmenu>Pogledi orodij</guisubmenu> imate seznam vseh omogočenih "
"vtičnikov. Kliknite potrditveno polje pred vsakim elementom ali kliknite z "
"&LMB; na gumbih orodij v stranski vrstici za vklop in izklop tega pogleda "
"orodja."

#. Tag: title
#: fundamentals.docbook:280
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shortcuts"
msgstr "Bližnjice"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:282
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Many of &kate;'s keystroke commands (shortcuts) are configurable by way of "
"the <link linkend=\"settings-help-menu\">Settings</link> menu. By default "
"&kate; honors the following key bindings."
msgstr ""
"Številne ukaze s tipkami &kate; (bližnjice) je mogoče konfigurirati v meniju "
"<link linkend=\"settings-help-menu\">Nastavitve</link>. Privzeto &kate; "
"upošteva naslednje vezave tipk."

#. Tag: keycap
#: fundamentals.docbook:293
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keycap>F1</keycap>"
msgstr "<keycap>F1</keycap>"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:294
#, no-c-format
msgid "Help"
msgstr "Pomoč"

#. Tag: keycombo
#: fundamentals.docbook:297
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Shift;<keycap>F1</keycap>"
msgstr "&Shift;<keycap>F1</keycap>"

#. Tag: link
#: fundamentals.docbook:298
#, no-c-format
msgid "What's this?"
msgstr "Kaj je to?"

#. Tag: keycombo
#: fundamentals.docbook:301
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap>"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:302
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"file-new\">New</link> document"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"file-new\">Nov</link> dokument"

#. Tag: keycombo
#: fundamentals.docbook:305
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;<keycap>L</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;<keycap>L</keycap>"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:306
