"\"help:/katepart/keybindings.html\">&katepart;</ulink> in vsi aktivirani "
"<link linkend=\"plugins\">&kate; vtičniki</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: fundamentals.docbook:385
#, no-c-format
msgid "Working With the &kate; <acronym>MDI</acronym>"
msgstr "Delo z &kate; <acronym>MDI</acronym>"

#. Tag: title
#: fundamentals.docbook:388
#, no-c-format
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "Pregled"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:390
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Window, View, Document, Frame, Editor... What are they all in the "
"terminology of &kate;, and how do you get the most out of it? This chapter "
"will explain all of that, and even more."
msgstr ""
"Okno, pogled, dokument, okvir, urejevalnik ... Kaj vse so v terminologiji "
"&kate; in kako to kar najbolje izkoristite? To poglavje bo pojasnilo vse to "
"in še več."

#. Tag: title
#: fundamentals.docbook:396
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Main Window"
msgstr "Glavno okno"

#. Tag: primary
#: fundamentals.docbook:398
#, no-c-format
msgid "Main window"
msgstr "Glavno okno"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:398
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &kate; Main Window is a standard &kde; application window, with the "
"addition of side bars containing tool views. It has a menubar with all the "
"common menus, and some more, and a toolbar providing access to commonly used "
"commands."
msgstr ""
"&kate; Glavno okno je standardni &kde; okno aplikacije z dodatkom stranskih "
"vrstic s pogledi orodij. Ima menijsko vrstico z vsemi običajnimi meniji in "
"nekaterimi več ter orodno vrstico, ki omogoča dostop do pogosto uporabljenih "
"ukazov."

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:404
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The most important part of the window is the editing area, by default "
"displaying a single text editor component, in which you can work with your "
"documents."
msgstr ""
"Najpomembnejši del okna je območje za urejanje, ki privzeto prikazuje eno "
"komponento urejevalnika besedila, v katerem lahko delate s svojimi dokumenti."

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:408
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The docking capabilities of the window is used for the tool windows of any "
"plugin enabled in the settings dialog."
msgstr ""
"Zmožnosti priklopa okna se uporabljajo za okna orodij katerega koli "
"vtičnika, omogočenega v pogovornem oknu z nastavitvami."

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:411
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Tool views can be positioned in any sidebar, to move a tool right click its "
"sidebar button and select from the &RMB; menu"
msgstr ""
"Poglede orodij je mogoče postaviti v katero koli stransko vrstico, če želite "
"premakniti orodje, z desno miškino tipko kliknite gumb na stranski vrstici "
"in izberite med &RMB; meni"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:414
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A tool view can be marked as <emphasis>persistent</emphasis> in the &RMB; "
"menu for its sidebar button. The sidebar can contain more tools at one time "
"so that when a tool is persistent other tools can be shown simultaneously."
msgstr ""
"Pogled orodja lahko označite kot <emphasis>obstojen</emphasis> v &RMB; meni "
"za gumb stranske vrstice. Stranska vrstica lahko vsebuje več orodij hkrati, "
"tako da so lahko hkrati prikazana druga orodja, ko je orodje obstojno."

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:419
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If a plugin has configuration options you can use the first item in the "
"context menu to open the corresponding page in &kate;'s settings dialog."
msgstr ""
"Če ima vtičnik konfiguracijske možnosti, lahko uporabite prvi element v "
"kontekstnem meniju, da odprete ustrezno stran v pogovornem oknu z "
"nastavitvami &kate;."

#. Tag: title
#: fundamentals.docbook:429
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Editor area"
msgstr "Območje urejevalnika"

#. Tag: primary
#: fundamentals.docbook:431
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editing Area"
msgstr "Območje urejanja"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:431
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kate; is capable of having more than one document open at the same time, "
"and also of splitting the editing area into any number of frames, similar to "
"how for example &konqueror; or the popular <application>emacs</application> "
"text editor works. This way you can view several documents at the same time, "
"or more instances of the same document, handy for example if your document "
"contains definitions in the top that you want to see often for reference. Or "
"you could view a program source header in one frame, while editing the "
"implementation file in another."
msgstr ""
"&kate; je sposoben imeti odprtih več kot en dokument hkrati in tudi "
"razdeliti območje urejanja na poljubno število okvirjev, podobno kot na "
"primer &konqueror; ali priljubljen urejevalnik besedil <application>emacs</"
"application> deluje. Na ta način si lahko ogledate več dokumentov hkrati ali "
"več primerkov istega dokumenta, kar je priročno na primer, če vaš dokument "
"vsebuje definicije na vrhu, ki jih želite pogosto videti za referenco. Lahko "
"pa si ogledate izvorno glavo programa v enem okviru, medtem ko urejate "
"implementacijsko datoteko v drugem."

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:442
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When a document is available in more than one editor, changes made in one "
"editor will immediately be reflected in the others as well. This includes "
"changing the text as well as selecting text. Search operations or cursor "
"movement is only reflected in the current editor."
msgstr ""
"Ko je dokument na voljo v več kot enem urejevalniku, bodo spremembe, "
"narejene v enem urejevalniku, takoj odražene tudi v drugih. To vključuje "
"spreminjanje besedila in izbiro besedila. Iskalne operacije ali premikanje "
"kazalca se odražajo samo v trenutnem urejevalniku."

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:448
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is currently not possible to have more instances of the same document "
"open in the sense that one instance will be edited while the other will not."
msgstr ""
"Trenutno ni mogoče imeti odprtih več primerkov istega dokumenta v smislu, da "
"bo en primerek urejen, drugi pa ne."

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:452
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When splitting an editor into two frames, it is divided into two equally "
"sized frames, both displaying the current document of that editor. The new "
"frame will be at the bottom (in the case of a horizontal split) or at the "
"right (for a vertical split). The new frame gets the focus, which is "
"visualized by the blinking cursor bar in the focused frame."
msgstr ""
"Pri razdelitvi urejevalnika na dva okvirja se ta razdeli na dva enako velika "
"okvirja, pri čemer oba prikazujeta trenutni dokument tega urejevalnika. Nov "
"okvir bo na dnu (pri vodoravni razcepu) ali na desni (pri navpični razcepu). "
"Nov okvir dobi fokus, ki je prikazan z utripajočo vrstico kazalca v fokusnem "
"okvirju."

#. Tag: title
#: fundamentals.docbook:464
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using Sessions"
msgstr "Uporaba Sessions"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:466
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sessions is how &kate; lets you keep more than one list of files and &GUI; "
"configuration around. You can have as many named sessions as you want, and "
"you can use unnamed or anonymous sessions for files you want to use only "
"once. Currently &kate; can save the list of open files, and the general "
"window configuration in the session; future versions of &kate; may add more "
"features that can be saved in sessions. With the introduction of sessions, "
"&kate; also allows you to open any number of instances of the application "
"instead of just one as it used to do as the default behavior."
msgstr ""
"Seje so, kako &kate; omogoča shranjevanje več kot enega seznama datotek in "
"&GUI; konfiguracijo okoli. Imate lahko toliko poimenovanih sej, kot želite, "
"in lahko uporabite neimenovane ali anonimne seje za datoteke, ki jih želite "
"uporabiti samo enkrat. Trenutno &kate; lahko shrani seznam odprtih datotek "
"in splošno konfiguracijo oken v seji; prihodnje različice &kate; lahko doda "
"več funkcij, ki jih je mogoče shraniti v sejah. Z uvedbo sej je &kate; prav "
"tako vam omogoča, da odprete poljubno število primerkov aplikacije namesto "
"samo enega, kot je bilo običajno privzeto."

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:475
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sessions are supported in three areas:"
msgstr "Seje so podprte na treh področjih:"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:478
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"command-line-options\"><emphasis>Command line options</"
"emphasis></link> that lets you select and start sessions when launching "
"&kate; from the command line."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"command-line-options\"><emphasis>Možnosti ukazne vrstice</"
"emphasis></link>, ki vam omogoča izbiro in začetek sej ob zagonu &kate; iz "
"ukazne vrstice."

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:482
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"sessions-menu\"><emphasis>The Sessions menu</emphasis></"
"link> that lets you switch, save, start and manage your sessions."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"sessions-menu\"><emphasis>Meni Seje</emphasis></link>, ki "
"vam omogoča preklapljanje, shranjevanje, začetek in upravljanje sej."

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:485
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"config-dialog-sessions\"><emphasis>Configuration options</"
"emphasis></link> that lets you decide how sessions generally should behave."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"config-dialog-sessions\"><emphasis>Možnosti konfiguracije</"
"emphasis></link>, ki vam omogočajo, da se odločite, kako naj se seje na "
"splošno obnašajo."

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:492
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When starting a new session, the &GUI; configuration of <guilabel>Default "
"Session</guilabel> is loaded. To save window configuration in the default "
"session, you need to enable saving window configuration in the sessions "
"configuration page of the configuration dialog and then load the default "
"session, set up the window as desired and save the session again."
msgstr ""
"Ko začnete novo sejo, &GUI; konfiguracija <guilabel>Privzete seje</guilabel> "
"je naložena. Če želite shraniti konfiguracijo okna v privzeti seji, morate "
"omogočiti shranjevanje konfiguracije okna na strani s konfiguracijo sej v "
"konfiguracijskem pogovornem oknu in nato naložiti privzeto sejo, nastaviti "
"okno po želji in znova shraniti sejo."

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:498
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When a named session is loaded, &kate; will display the session name at the "
"start of the window title, which then has the form "
"<quote><replaceable>Session Name</replaceable>: <replaceable>Document name "
"or &URL;</replaceable> - &kate;</quote>."
msgstr ""
"Ko se naloži imenovana seja, &kate; bo prikazalo ime seje na začetku naslova "
"okna, ki ima nato obliko <quote><replaceable>Ime seje</replaceable>: "
"<replaceable>Ime dokumenta ali &URL;</replaceable> - &kate;</quote> ."

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:503
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When opening files on the command line with <option>--start "
"<replaceable>name</replaceable></option> or if a session is selected using "
"the session chooser, the specified session is loaded prior to the files "
"specified on the command line. To open files from the command line in a new, "
"unnamed session, configure &kate; to start a new session as default in the "
"session page of the configuration dialog or use <option>--start</option> "
"with an empty string: <replaceable>''</replaceable>."
msgstr ""
"Pri odpiranju datotek v ukazni vrstici z <option>--start <replaceable>ime</"
"replaceable></option> ali če je seja izbrana z izbirnikom seje, se navedena "
"seja naloži pred datotekami, določenimi v ukazu linija. Če želite odpreti "
"datoteke iz ukazne vrstice v novi, neimenovani seji, konfigurirajte &kate; "
"da začnete novo sejo kot privzeto na strani seje konfiguracijskega "
"pogovornega okna ali uporabite <option>--start</option> s praznim nizom: "
"<replaceable>''</replaceable>."

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:511
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Since &kate; 2.5.1 the <acronym>PID</acronym> of the current instance is "
"exported to the environment variable <envar>KATE_PID</envar>. When opening "
"files from the built in terminal Kate will automatically select the current "
"instance if nothing else is indicated on the command line."
msgstr ""
"Ker &kate; 2.5.1 <acronym>PID</acronym> trenutnega primerka se izvozi v "
"spremenljivko okolja <envar>KATE_PID</envar>. Pri odpiranju datotek iz "
"vgrajenega terminala bo Kate samodejno izbral trenutni primerek, če v ukazni "
"vrstici ni navedeno nič drugega."

#. Tag: title
#: fundamentals.docbook:519
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Quick Open</title>"
msgstr "<title>Hitro odpiranje</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:521
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To be able to quickly open/switch between files, Kate comes with a built-in "
"quick open dialog. You can open it with <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"&Alt;<keycap>O</keycap></keycombo>."
msgstr ""
"Za hitro odpiranje/preklapljanje med datotekami ima Kate vgrajeno pogovorno "
"okno za hitro odpiranje. Odprete ga lahko s <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"&Alt;<keycap>O</keycap></keycombo>."

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:525
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Quick open can show all open documents in Kate as well as all files in open "
"projects. To be able to see project files, you need to enable <link linkend="
"\"kate-application-plugin-projects\">Project Plugin</link>."
msgstr ""
"Hitro odpiranje lahko prikaže vse odprte dokumente v Kate kot tudi vse "
"datoteke v odprtih projektih. Če si želite ogledati projektne datoteke, "
"morate omogočiti <link linkend=\"kate-application-plugin-projects"
"\">projektni vtičnik</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: fundamentals.docbook:531
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using Quick Open"
msgstr "Uporaba Hitrega odpiranja"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:533
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Using quick open is very simple. Once you open it, just type the name or "
"portions of the name of the file you want to open and quick open will filter "
"the list based on what you typed. Hitting &Enter; opens the selected file, "
"while &Esc; hides the quick open."
msgstr ""
"Uporaba hitrega odpiranja je zelo preprosta. Ko jo odprete, samo vnesite ime "
"ali dele imena datoteke, ki jo želite odpreti, in hitro odpiranje bo "
"filtriralo seznam glede na to, kar ste vnesli. Pritisnite &Enter; odpre "
"izbrano datoteko, &Esc; skrije hitro odpiranje."

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:538
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default, only the file name is matched while filtering. If you want to "
"match path, you need to have a \"/\" in the typed text. For example: \"doc/"
"index\" will match all the files that contain \"index\" inside the folder "
"\"doc\"."
msgstr ""
"Med filtriranjem se privzeto ujema samo ime datoteke. Če želite ujemati pot, "
"morate v vnesenem besedilu imeti \"/\". Na primer: \"doc/index\" se bo "
"ujemal z vsemi datotekami, ki vsebujejo \"index\" v mapi \"doc\"."

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:543
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The documents which are already open are highlighted in bold and are listed "
"at the top when the dialog opens. Also, when quick open shows up the "
"previous open document is already selected so you can just press &Enter; and "
"it will take you to that document."
msgstr ""
"Dokumenti, ki so že odprti, so označeni s krepkim tiskom in so navedeni na "
"vrhu, ko se odpre pogovorno okno. Poleg tega, ko se prikaže hitro odpiranje, "
"je prejšnji odprt dokument že izbran, tako da lahko samo pritisnete &Enter; "
"in popeljal vas bo do tega dokumenta."

#. Tag: title
#: fundamentals.docbook:552
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring Quick Open"
msgstr "Konfiguriranje hitrega odpiranja"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: fundamentals.docbook:554
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Quick Open</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Hitro odpiranje</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:559
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Quick open provides a couple of config options. To access these options, "
"right-click in the input line edit."
msgstr ""
"Hitro odpiranje ponuja nekaj možnosti konfiguracije. Za dostop do teh "
"možnosti z desno miškino tipko kliknite urejanje vnosne vrstice."

#. Tag: term
#: fundamentals.docbook:564
#, no-c-format
msgid "Currently available options are:"
msgstr "Trenutno razpoložljive možnosti so:"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:566
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>Current Project</userinput> - Show files from current project only"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>Trenutni projekt</userinput> - Prikaži samo datoteke trenutnega "
"projekta"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:567
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>All Projects</userinput> - Show files from all open projects"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>Vsi projekti</userinput> – Prikaži datoteke iz vseh odprtih "
"projektov"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:568
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>Fuzzy Filtering</userinput> - Use fuzzy matching algorithm to "
"filter files"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>Mehko filtriranje</userinput> - za filtriranje datotek uporabite "
"algoritem mehkega ujemanja"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:569
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>Wildcard Filtering</userinput>- Use wildcard matching to filter "
"files"
msgstr ""
"<userinput>Filtriranje z nadomestnimi znaki</userinput> – za filtriranje "
"datotek uporabite ujemanje z nadomestnimi znaki"

#. Tag: title
#: fundamentals.docbook:579
#, no-c-format
msgid "Getting Help"
msgstr "Iskanje pomoči"

#. Tag: title
#: fundamentals.docbook:583
#, no-c-format
msgid "With &kate;"
msgstr "Z &kate;"

#. Tag: term
#: fundamentals.docbook:587
#, no-c-format
msgid "This manual"
msgstr "Ta priročnik"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:590
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Offers detailed documentation on all menu commands, configuration options, "
"tools, dialogs, plugins &etc; as well as descriptions of the &kate; window, "
"the editor and various concepts used in the application."
msgstr ""
"Ponuja podrobno dokumentacijo o vseh menijskih ukazih, konfiguracijskih "
"možnostih, orodjih, pogovornih oknih, vtičnikih &etc; kot tudi opise &kate; "
"okno, urejevalnik in različne koncepte, ki se uporabljajo v aplikaciji."

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:595
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press <keycap>F1</keycap> or use the <menuchoice><guimenu>Help</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>&kate; Handbook</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu topic to view "
"this manual."
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite <keycap>F1</keycap> ali uporabite <menuchoice><guimenu>Pomoč</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>&kate; Priročnik</guimenuitem></menuchoice> tema "
"menija za ogled tega priročnika."

#. Tag: term
#: fundamentals.docbook:603
#, no-c-format
msgid "What's This Help"
msgstr "Kaj je to pomoč"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:605
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"What's This help offers immediate help with single elements of graphical "
"windows, such as buttons or other window areas."
msgstr ""
"Kaj je ta pomoč ponuja takojšnjo pomoč pri posameznih elementih grafičnih "
"oken, kot so gumbi ali druga področja oken."

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:608
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"We strive to provide What's This help for any elements for which it makes "
"sense. It is available throughout the configuration dialog, and in many "
"other dialogs as well."
msgstr ""
"Prizadevamo si zagotoviti pomoč Kaj je to za vse elemente, za katere je to "
"smiselno. Na voljo je v celotnem konfiguracijskem pogovornem oknu in tudi v "
"mnogih drugih pogovornih oknih."

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:612
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To employ What's This help, press <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;"
"<keycap>F1</keycap></keycombo> or use the <menuchoice><guimenu>Help</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>What's This</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item to "
"enable What's This mode. The cursor will turn into an arrow with a question "
"mark, and you can now click any element in the window to read the What's "
"This help for that element, if it is available."
msgstr ""
"Če želite uporabiti pomoč Kaj je to, pritisnite <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Shift;<keycap>F1</keycap></keycombo> ali uporabite "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu><guimenuitem>Kaj je to</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> element menija za omogočanje načina Kaj je to. Kazalec se bo "
"spremenil v puščico z vprašajem in zdaj lahko kliknete kateri koli element v "
"oknu, da preberete pomoč Kaj je to za ta element, če je na voljo."

#. Tag: term
#: fundamentals.docbook:623
#, no-c-format
msgid "Help Buttons in Dialogs"
msgstr "Gumbi za pomoč v pogovornih oknih"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:625
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some dialogs have a <guibutton>Help</guibutton> Button. Pressing it will "
"start the &khelpcenter; and open the relevant documentation."
msgstr ""
"Nekatera pogovorna okna imajo gumb <guibutton>Pomoč</guibutton>. Če ga "
"pritisnete, se zažene &khelpcenter; in odprite ustrezno dokumentacijo."

#. Tag: title
#: fundamentals.docbook:635
#, no-c-format
msgid "With Your Text Files"
msgstr "Z vašimi besedilnimi datotekami"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:637
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kate; does not (yet!) provide any means for reading document related "
"documentation. Depending on the file you are editing, you may find the <link "
"linkend=\"kate-application-plugin-konsole\">Built in Terminal Emulator</"
"link> helpful for viewing related &UNIX; manual pages or info documentation, "
"or you can use &konqueror;."
msgstr ""
"&kate; (še!) ne ponuja nobenega sredstva za branje dokumentacije, povezane z "
"dokumenti. Odvisno od datoteke, ki jo urejate, vam bo <link linkend=\"kate-"
"application-plugin-konsole\">vgrajeni terminalski emulator</link> morda v "
"pomoč pri ogledovanju povezanih &UNIX; strani s priročnikom ali "
"informacijsko dokumentacijo ali pa uporabite &konqueror;."

#. Tag: title
#: fundamentals.docbook:646
#, no-c-format
msgid "Articles on &kate;"
msgstr "Članki o &kate;"

#. Tag: para
#: fundamentals.docbook:648
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kate;'s homepage provides some <ulink url=\"https://kate-editor.org/"
"featured-articles\"> Articles and Howtos</ulink> with further information "
"beyond the scope of this handbook."
msgstr ""
"Domača stran &kate; ponuja nekaj <ulink url=\"https://kate-editor.org/"
"featured-articles\"> člankov in navodil</ulink> z dodatnimi informacijami, "
"ki presegajo obseg tega priročnika."

